{"tid":1189650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙移交94名台灣電訊網絡詐騙疑犯到北京　","createTime":"2019-06-07T01:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T04:23:57.000Z","uid":37554,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5d741f7a7cee07f3645ac673074cb35fe7cc8288","tid":1189650,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:31:13.000Z","msg":"西班牙移交94名電訊網絡詐騙案疑犯到北京。<br />\n<br />\n公安在2016年上半年發現，西班牙境內有不法份子，大規劃詐騙內地民眾，出現多宗損失千萬元人民幣以上的重大案件。兩地警方合作調查後，鎖定多個疑犯藏身地點，同年底在馬德里、巴塞羅那及阿利坎特，拘捕2百多人。<br />\n<br />\n截至目前為止，西班牙政府共批准北京引渡225人，當中包括已被押解的131人，及本月6日從馬德里押解出發的94人。被押解到內地的疑犯，大部分來自台灣。"},{"pid":"068164858a5fb3f1db5ee956fdf635f521935734","tid":1189650,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmY1Du8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmY1Du8.jpg&h=6ddcf26c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da093a455024d22149ebcedf601ceaf4fa53bc3c","tid":1189650,"uid":50835,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"垃圾歐豬國"},{"pid":"3334687783f2302ab340bb428cc3eab840a692ab","tid":1189650,"uid":119695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">西班牙境內有不法份子，大規劃詐騙內地民眾。</span><br />\n去到外國都係呃返蝗國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7e7d0434e71aa3d327d4cde0d6fb5b16274bf9","tid":1189650,"uid":98904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3334687783f2302ab340bb428cc3eab840a692ab","tid":1189650,"uid":119695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">西班牙境內有不法份子，大規劃詐騙內地民眾。</span><br />\n去到外國都係呃返蝗國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"佢哋識鳩講英文西班牙文咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a818f84673f185269fbd04a